description:
Visual Basic & SQL program

Database program storing information of training center

  • Internal (Employee & Instructors).
  • All Courses Data.
  • Active Courses with all its information:

Dates , Duration & Students

Administrator can block and unblock students for certain time interval.

Each video lecture have its source code.
This course will give you solid understanding of using SQL- Server Database with VB.net application.

- This Course will Take 5 hours For average user.
title: VB.net & SQL
